item.description:
Hi all,

We had so much fun yesterday we thought this would be a great course to go to again. It is fun, beautiful and in great condition. I know it is labor day weekend, but if you are around - try to join.

I have two tee times one at 9:50 and one at 10:00.

$60 for 18 and cart.

It is a bit of a hike so please let us know if you are interested in carpooling when you respond.

Hope to see you there.

Amy
